title: Poena is Koning (2007)
description:
South African Afrikaans Movie

Two buddies decide that they cannot leave school as virgins. Unfortunately, they embark on this quest during the final matric exam, which causes a major distraction from their studies and has dire consequences. Juffrou Muller, one of the teachers in the school comes to their aid, but all the two heroes want to do is to jump their teacher, who is both flattered and quite in favour of the idea. Our hero then gets arrested for indecent exposure, having to complete his matric exams in handcuffs. He later pursues his dream to become a pop star with his band, trying their luck internationally, with surprising results. During all this he still seeks to get laid, and eventually falls in love.
